        <section name="What/Why?">
            <dl>
                <dt>What is the motivation for these features?</dt>
                <dd><a href="http://dev.day.com/docs/en/cq/current/javadoc/com/day/cq/wcm/api/PageFilter.html">PageFilter</a>
                    is limiting and makes a number of assumptions. The result
                    of those assumptions in the professional services field
                    is often re-creating navigation and sitemap components.
                </dd>
                
                <dt>What does this provide that isn't out-of-box?</dt>
                <dd>Implementations of Filter&lt;Page&gt; that provide static
                    instances that maintain some assumptions but also provide
                    some flexibility to developers and designers.</dd>
                
